com.interpss.opf.datatype

Interface OpfDatatypePackage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.ENamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OpfDatatypePackageImpl

    public interface OpfDatatypePackage
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EPackage
    The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
    Interpss power system simulation framework OPF/Constraint package. It defines classes for OPF Contraint.
    See Also:
    OpfDatatypeFactory
